Add ability to define custom segments in a `config.json` file as shown below:
```
{
  "segments": [
    "/Users/xxx/.config/powerline-shell/segments/my_segment.py",
    "username"
  ],
  "theme": "/Users/xxx/.config/powerline-shell//themes/my_theme.py"
}
```

